                                                      anyway,
                                                      but this
                                                      is  a
                                                      better
                                                      choice
                                                      for
                                                      compatibility
                                                      with
                                                      other
                                                      implementations.

                                               ----iinnppuutt--ffdd
                                               _f_d
                                                      Read
                                                      keyboard
                                                      input
                                                      from the
                                                      given
                                                      file
                                                      descrip‐
                                                      tor.
                                                      Most
                                                      ddiiaalloogg
                                                      scripts
                                                      read
                                                      from  the
                                                      standard
                                                      input,
                                                      but the
                                                      gauge
                                                      widget
