                                                      a pipe
                                                      (which
                                                      is
                                                      always
                                                      standard
                                                      input).
                                                      Some
                                                      configurations
                                                      do  not
                                                      work
                                                      properly
                                                      when
                                                      ddiiaa‐‐
                                                      lloogg
