                                                      connected
                                                      by
                                                      "----aanndd--wwiiddggeett",
                                                      it clears
                                                      the  old
                                                      widget
                                                      from
                                                      the
                                                      screen
                                                      by
                                                      painting
                                                      over  it.
                                                      Use this
                                                      option to
                                                      suppress
                                                      that
                                                      repainting.

                                                      At exit,
                                                      ddiiaalloogg
                                                      repaints
                                                      all
                                                      of the
                                                      widgets
                                                      which
                                                      have
                                                      been
                                                      marked
                                                      with
                                                      "----kkeeeepp--wwiinnddooww",
                                                      even
