                                               ----nnoo--ccoollllaappssee
                                                      Normally
                                                      ddiiaalloogg
                                                      converts
                                                      tabs   to
                                                      spaces
                                                      and
                                                      reduces
                                                      multiple
                                                      spaces to
                                                      a  single
                                                      space
                                                      for text
                                                      which is
                                                      displayed
                                                      in a
