                                                      Use  this
                                                      option
                                                      to dis‐
                                                      able that
                                                      feature.
                                                      Note that
                                                      ddiiaalloogg
                                                      will
                                                      still
                                                      wrap
                                                      text,
                                                      subject
                                                      to the
                                                      "----ccrr--wwrraapp"
                                                      and
                                                      "----ttrriimm"
                                                      options.

                                               ----nnoo--kkiillll
                                                      Tells
                                                      ddiiaalloogg
                                                      to
                                                      put  the
